issue.title: Place where the invited person puts in their information
How will the invites happen? Think about how will a person send an invitation to another.
issue.body:
Send a link that the recipient can follow back to the trip page in order to enter their info and keep moving the coordination workflow forward.

We should be able to send the link via whatever info they gave us:
- phone number: use twilio api to send link
- email: duh

Link route needs to have a token to lead back to the trip.
